  "short_description": "IP66 weatherproof arm mount for G5 Turret Ultra camera. Supports 3/4\" conduit. Extends camera away from mounting surface for wider field of view. Constructed with aluminium and polycarbonate.",
  "description": "Expand your surveillance capabilities with the Ubiquiti Camera Arm Mount, designed specifically for the G5 Turret Ultra camera. This weatherproof accessory allows achieving optimal positioning for your camera, enhancing your monitoring range and effectiveness. Mount your G5 Turret Ultra camera on walls, corners, or poles, providing greater flexibility in positioning the camera for the best possible view of your desired area. With the Ubiquiti Camera Arm Mount, you can unlock the full potential of your G5 Turret Ultra camera, achieving optimal camera placement for comprehensive monitoring.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Arm Mount for G5 Turret Ultra",
      "text": "Expand your surveillance capabilities with the Ubiquiti Camera Arm Mount, designed specifically for the G5 Turret Ultra camera. This weatherproof accessory allows achieving optimal positioning for your camera, enhancing your monitoring range and effectiveness. Mount your G5 Turret Ultra camera on walls, corners, or poles, providing greater flexibility in positioning the camera for the best possible view of your desired area. With the Ubiquiti Camera Arm Mount, you can unlock the full potential of your G5 Turret Ultra camera, achieving optimal camera placement for comprehensive monitoring."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Secure Installation",
      "text": "The arm mount supports 3/4\" conduit, simplifying cable management and ensuring a secure connection between your camera and the network. By extending the camera away from the mounting surface, the arm mount allows for a wider field of view, ensuring you capture crucial details within your monitored space. Constructed with weatherproof materials, the Camera Arm Mount is built to endure harsh outdoor conditions, making it ideal for year-round use."
    }
  ],
